      "type": "pre",
      "text": "=> fact(5)\n=> 5 * fact(4)\n=> 5 * (4 * fact(3))\n=> 5 * (4 * (3 * fact(2)))\n=> 5 * (4 * (3 * (2 * fact(1))))\n=> 5 * (4 * (3 * (2 * 1)))\n=> 5 * (4 * (3 * 2))\n=> 5 * (4 * 6)\n=> 5 * 24\n=> 120"
